      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it's been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super well-loved, so it's totally ready for its next big adventure with you! Everything runs smoothly, it looks great, and it's just a reliable, comfy car for getting around. If you\u2019re looking for something dependable that\u2019s been taken care of, this is the one. Drop me a message if you want to come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
