    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2008 Porsche 911 Carrera S represents a highly visceral, analog driving experience. Powered by the 3.8L M97 flat-six engine paired with a crisp G97 6-speed manual transaxle, it delivers 355 hp with a linear power band. The chassis features Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) for optimized damping and a factory-spec limited-slip differential for superior corner-exit traction. This example has been meticulously maintained mechanically, with a recent bore-scope inspection confirming cylinder wall integrity. Though it displays minor cosmetic road patina, the drivetrain remains tight, the synchros are flawless, and the hydraulic steering feedback is superlative. A true driver's car ready for the canyons.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
