    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic balance of performance and practicality, having been meticulously maintained by its current owner. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish, with only minor road wear and small stone chips consistent with careful use. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean; the premium leather seats remain supple, and all electronic features\u2014including the infotainment system and dual-zone climate control\u2014function perfectly. Mechanically, the car is in robust health, benefiting from a documented service history that includes a recent brake overhaul and a fresh synthetic oil change. It starts promptly, idles smoothly, and provides a responsive, quiet driving experience. Whether you\u2019re looking for a reliable daily commuter or a comfortable long-distance cruiser, this car is ready for the road with no immediate maintenance required. This is a non-smoker vehicle that has been primarily garaged.",
      "price": 34500.0,
